---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MainHeader from '../components/common/MainHeader.astro';
---

<Layout
    title='Terms of Service - KASANE - è¥²'
    description='Read our terms of service regarding the use of KASANE.'
    type='website'
    url='https://kasane-palette.dev/terms'
>
    <div class='flex flex-col min-h-screen'>
        <main class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20'>
            <MainHeader
                mainTitle='Terms of Service'
                subTitle='Rules & Regulations'
            />

            <div class='space-y-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-stone-700'>
                <div
                    class='prose prose-stone leading-loose text-stone-600 space-y-6'
                >
                    <p>
                        Welcome to KASANE. By accessing this website, you agree
                        to be bound by these Terms of Service. Please read them
                        carefully before using our tools.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <section class='space-y-6'>
                    <h2
                        class='text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3'
                    >
                        <span class='w-8 h-px bg-stone-300'></span>
                        1. Usage License
                    </h2>
                    <div
                        class='bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-4'
                    >
                        <p class='text-stone-600 leading-relaxed'>
                            KASANE is an open-source tool designed for
                            developers and designers. You are free to use the
                            color palettes, code snippets (JSON, CSS, SVG), and
                            patterns generated by this website for both
                            <strong>personal and commercial projects</strong> without
                            attribution (though it is appreciated).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class='space-y-6'>
                    <h2
                        class='text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3'
                    >
                        <span class='w-8 h-px bg-stone-300'></span>
                        2. Disclaimer
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-stone-600 leading-relaxed'>
                        The materials and tools on KASANE are provided on an 'as
                        is' basis. While we strive for accuracy in color
                        conversion and code generation (Shopify Liquid, Tailwind
                        CSS, etc.),
                        <strong>we make no warranties</strong> regarding the reliability
                        or suitability of the generated code for your specific environment.
                    </p>
                    <p class='text-stone-600 leading-relaxed'>
                        We shall not be held liable for any damages arising from
                        the use of our tools, including but not limited to theme
                        conflicts, display errors, or data loss.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class='space-y-6'>
                    <h2
                        class='text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3'
                    >
                        <span class='w-8 h-px bg-stone-300'></span>
                        3. Limitations
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-stone-600 leading-relaxed'>
                        Since KASANE operates as a client-side application, your
                        settings and history are stored locally in your browser.
                        We are not responsible for any data loss that occurs if
                        you clear your browser cache or if local storage is
                        corrupted.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class='space-y-6'>
                    <h2
                        class='text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3'
                    >
                        <span class='w-8 h-px bg-stone-300'></span>
                        4. Governing Law
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-stone-600 leading-relaxed'>
                        These terms and conditions are governed by and construed
                        in accordance with the laws of Japan.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class='border-t border-stone-200 pt-10'>
                    <p class='text-sm text-stone-400 text-center'>
                        Last updated: {
                            new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
                                year: 'numeric',
                                month: 'long',
                                day: 'numeric',
                            })
                        }
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>
